title: When did the S8 finish?
body:
I have checked the end of S8 is 23:59 12 Nov , but nothing happen when i login today. I want ori skin!!!!!
when can i get it?

replies.body: The season rewards will be handed out over the coming weeks, but because of the sheer scale of it all it's not going to be an instantaneous "drop", some players will get their rewards before others, though no one will get them right away. As per the ["End-Of-Season Information" Support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/360010365913-End-of-season-information), rewards should be out by the 12th of December, so if you haven't got rewards by then you'll want to submit a ticket to [Support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) (use the "2018 Season Ranked and Honor rewards" option).
